#
KAKASHI’S BAR – NIGHT[p]
Sasuke remembers that they used to hang fairy lights on the wall… back when this bar used to be a cheap, university café.[p]
There used to be an unpainted and unplastered cement wall with flickering fairy lights hanging from above. [p]
A chalkboard menu was in the middle and it was framed by pots of plastic plants. [p]

[_tb_end_text]

[tb_image_show  time="1000"  storage="default/whisky.jpg"  width="1280"  height="720"  name="img_8"  ]
