#Sasuke Uchiha
Pretty enough if you squint, that’s what Sakura liked so much. She said… [p]
What was it? Stars?[p]
Stars![p]
Sakura said they looked like twinkling stars. I thought they were just faulty, flickering in and out because they were old.[p]
In any case… they’re gone. Just like her.[p]

[_tb_end_text]

